My name is Yoshikana Karna. I'm 33 years old. My house is in the northeast section of Pune, where all the villas are, and I am not married. I work as an employee for the Big  BAZAAR department stores, and I get home every day by 8 PM at the latest. I don't smoke, but I occasionally drink. I'm in bed by 11 PM, and make sure I get eight hours of sleep, no matter what. After having a glass of kesar warm milk and doing about twenty minutes of stretches before going to bed, I usually have no problems sleeping until morning. Just like a baby, I wake up without any fatigue or stress in the morning. I was told there were no issues at my last check-up. I'm trying to explain that I'm a person who wishes to live a very quiet life. I take care not to trouble myself with any enemies, like winning and losing, that would cause me to lose sleep at night. That is how I deal with society, and I know that is what brings me happiness. Although, if I were to fight I wouldn't lose to anyone.Jai Hind

En peyar Yoshikage kira. Ennaku 33 vayadhu. Annaithu villa kalum ulla, Morioh vin Vadakilaku pagudhiyil en vidu ulladhu. Enaku thirumanam aagavillai. Naan 'Kaama Yu' ennum Department Store il paniyalar aaga panipurigiren. Dhinamum, Eravu 8 manikul vidu thirumbi viduven. Naan pugai pidika maaten, Aanal epol aavudhu kudipen. Naan iravu 11 manikul padukai il padupen, Edhuvaga irundhalum naan 8 mani neram kattaiyam urangugiren endru urudhi seidhu kolven. 
Oru Glass vedhu vedhuvana paalai kudhithu vitu, summar 20 nimidathirku padupathirku moon udal payirchi seidhal, Endha prechanai yum illamal thoonga mudiyum. Oru kolandhaiyai polave, Kaalai il endha sorvum illamal, Mana aluthamum illamal Elundhukolven. Enadhu moonal Udal Nilai Sodhanai il endhu pirachanaigalum kandu pidika vilai. Naan migavum Amaidhiyana vaalkai ai vaala virumbum nabar endru vilaka muyargiren. 
Edhirigal, Vetri, Tholvi enna enadhu thookathai illaka veikum pirachanaigalai naan mudindha alavirku thavirka muyalven. Ivagaiyile naan Samudhayaithai kaiaaluven, Ivaigai vaalvu dhaan ennaku magilchi tharugiradhu endrum naangu ariven. Aanal, Naan yarrudan aavadhu sandai poda vendrum endral, Naan yaar idamum thorka maaten.

En per Yoshikage kira. Ennaku 33 vayasu. Ella villa vum irukara, Morioh vora Vadakilaku pagudhila en vidu irukudhu. Enaku kalyanam aagala. Naa 'Kaama Yu' ra Department Store la Kaikooli aaga velayseiren. Dhenamu, Rathiri 8 manikula vittuku thirumbi vandhruven. Naan dham adika maaten, Aanal epovachu saraku adipen. Naa rathiri 11 manikula enna vaanalum paduthruven, Edhuva irundhalum naa 8 mani nero kandipa thongren nu urudhi senjupen. 
Oru Glass vedhu vedhunra paala kudichitu, summar 20 nimisathuku padukarthuku moonala exercise seivve, Endha prechanai yum illama thoonguven. Oru kolandhaiya pola, Kaalai la endha tired um illama, stress illama Endhirpen. Ennora Health checkup la endha pirachanaiyum kandu pidikala. Naan romba Amaidhiyana vaalkai ah vaala virumbaravan nu solla try panren. 
Edhiri, Vetri, Tholvi nu enaora thookatha illaka vekra pirachanai ella naan mudinja alavuku avoid pannuven. Ippadidhaan ooru ulagatha samalikren, Indha maari vaalradhu dhaan ennaku sandhosam thardhu num ennaku nalla theriyum. Aana, Naan yartyachu panchayathu nu vantu, naan yaartayum thokka maaten radhu la theliva irruken.
